### Update Product Details

This endpoint allows the client to update the details of a specific product.

#### Request Body
- `name` (text) - The name of the product.
- `description` (text) - The description of the product.
- `category` (text) - The category of the product.
- `price` (text) - The price of the product.
- `stock` (text) - The total stock of the product.
- `availableStock` (text) - The available stock of the product.
- `tags[0]` (text) - Tag 1 for the product.
- `tags[1]` (text) - Tag 2 for the product.
- `tags[2]` (text) - Tag 3 for the product.
- `coverImage` (file) - The cover image of the product.
- `images` (file) - Additional images of the product.
- `deletedImages` (text) - Description of deleted images.

#### Response (200 - OK)
```json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "status": {"type": "string"},
        "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
                "_id": {"type": "string"},
                "name": {"type": "string"},
                "description": {"type": "string"},
                "category": {"type": "string"},
                "coverImage": {"type": "string"},
                "images": {
                    "type": "array",
